
@author @2026 John Paul Valenzuela

Standard pixl naming conventions:

use snake cases for instances but keep the normal camel case for the object:

    (sample)                    <Object> instance_1
    (project sample)            GL41Renderer gl41_renderer

use full descriptive function names dont't simplify all things:

    (sample)                    <return value> <function name>
    (project sample)            int get_entity_uniform();


